Andrea Pirlo scored a stunning free-kick for Juventus against Torino . 
 However, Juve fell to a 2-1 defeat and missed the chance to wrap up their fourth consecutive Serie A title . 
 Despite the loss, Juve remain 14 points clear at the top of the league table . 
 Pirlo is still playing at the top of his game at 35-years-old . 
 